(defcustom consult-omni-pubmed-api-key nil
  "Key for Pubmed Entrez API.

See URL `https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK25501/' for more info"
  :group 'consult-omni
  :type '(choice (const :tag "API Key" string)
